[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care-coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and consent, longitudinal-store initialization, channel entry with disclosure, input safety screening with continuous escalation screening, identity-and-context loading with multi-system integration, conversation handling with care-pathway-grounded responses, output safety screening with companion-pattern detection, warm-handoff routing to nurse care managers when applicable, care-team reporting with consent enforcement, and audit logging with care-coordination-specific retention discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (multi-system integration depth as architectural primitive, care-pathway-corpus governance with care-management-and-clinical-leadership ownership, care-transition protocol discipline, operational-service-level-aware coordination, and consent-aware multi-source information sharing).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolls via institution app, payer-benefits    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    portal, post-discharge workflow, or care-team          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    referral]                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent specific to care-coordination-AI  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      interaction with clinical-leadership and             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      legal-counsel-reviewed language                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Explicit non-care-manager disclosure acknowledged    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-system data-access consent collected per       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      source (EHR, HIE, pharmacy, ADT, connected devices,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      partner institutions)                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team sharing consent collected per care-team    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      role (PCP, specialists, nurse care manager,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pharmacist, home health, post-acute)                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - State-specific consent variations enforced where     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      sensitive-condition information has enhanced privacy │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      protections (42 CFR Part 2 for substance-use         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      treatment, state-specific reproductive-health rules, │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      state-specific behavioral-health rules)              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; enrollment confirmation;│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    initialization of longitudinal store]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE INITIALIZATION ─────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-assistant longitudinal store]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions on the problem list                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Current medications across pharmacies                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care plans and care-plan goals                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open referrals and their lifecycle states            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled appointments across institution            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent care transitions (admit, discharge, ED visits)│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent labs and imaging results                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team membership and roles                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Social-determinant-flag history                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated patient preferences                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient activation level (PAM-style stratification)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent posture across sources and roles             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables with care-          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordination-specific encryption keys                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent-context summary: cached, refreshed per        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive-disclosure surface: separately governed,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      restricted access                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for coordination      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    conversations]                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY WITH DISCLOSURE ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-initiated entry]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - In-app chat (most common)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS (where supported, with TCPA consent)             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Web chat                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel (where supported, with accessibility   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and disclosure considerations)                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Assistant-initiated entry, with care]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-pathway-milestone-driven (referral placed,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appointment booked, hospital admit, hospital         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      discharge, ED visit, lab result returned, medication │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      change order signed)                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Service-level-expectation-driven (referral aging     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      beyond institutional service-level expectation,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appointment within 24 hours requiring preparation)   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pattern-driven (patient repeatedly mentions specific │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      navigation difficulty)                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-requested (care manager requests           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      assistant to engage with patient about specific      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordination need)                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disclosure refresh per session or per defined cadence] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm a chat tool, not a person"                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm not a nurse and I'm not a care manager"         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I work alongside your care team to help you         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      navigate your care"                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "If you want to talk to a person, you can ask any    │
