[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    477[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient explicitly requests human                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    478[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination complexity exceeds assistant scope      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    479[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Concerning trajectory or pattern                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    480[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive disclosure pattern detected                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    481[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute symptom requiring triage                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    482[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mental-health-crisis indicators                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    483[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mandatory-reporting-relevant disclosure              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    484[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot confidence below threshold                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    485[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Service-level-expectation breach requiring care-team │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    486[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      action                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    487[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    488[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Handoff targets]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    489[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active emergency: 911 with stay-on-the-line guidance │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    490[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute symptom requiring triage: triage workflow      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    491[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      handoff with conversation context                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    492[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mental-health crisis: mental-health-bot or crisis    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    493[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pathway                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    494[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination complexity: nurse care manager (warm    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    495[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      handoff with full care-journey context)              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    496[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Service-level breach: operations or care-management  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    497[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      team                                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    498[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive disclosure: appropriate routing per        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    499[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      institutional policy                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    500[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team handoff (consent-gated): notify patient's  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    501[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      PCP, specialist, pharmacist, or other care-team      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    502[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      member                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    503[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    504[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Warm-handoff payload]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    505[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent conversation transcript                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    506[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-journey context summary                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    507[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open referrals, scheduled appointments, recent       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    508[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      transitions, recent labs                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    509[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Trigger reason                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient's preferred contact method                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    511[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient's stated preferences                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    512[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Assistant's structured summary                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    513[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    514[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bridge-and-stay pattern]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    515[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Assistant does not just hand patient a phone number  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    516[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Assistant bridges to human within the platform       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    517[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Assistant stays present until human has joined       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    518[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient does not start over                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    520[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    521[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: handoff event with structured payload to       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    522[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    appropriate target, conversation continuity preserved] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    523[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
