[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Correlate engagement with appointment-completion     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    551[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      rates, referral-closure rates, time-to-first-        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    552[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      specialist-visit, post-discharge readmission rates,  │
